      "text": "Schee arridsan gahje aug-\nscham/ Mitels/ Melaks/ Tel-\nArsus/ Kernbs/ Addons/ Im-\nmers/ bet tee ne warreja fawa\nTehwa Nammu parahdiht/nedeß\nfawu Dsimmumu/ arrig tee no\nIsraëta buhtu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 60,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Delajus Behrni/ Tohi-\njasa Behrni/ Nekoda Behrni/\nfeshfimts peezdeﬁmits un diwi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 61,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no to Preesteru Behr-\nncein/ Abajus Behrni/ Akoza\nBehrni/ Barsillaja Behrni/ kas\nno Barsillaja ta Gileaditera\nMeitahin bij Seewu nehmis/ un\ntappe pehz winxo Wahrdn deh-\nwehts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 62,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schee mekleja fawus\nRaddu-Rakſtus starp teem/kas\nRaddu-Rakſtōs bija usshimeti/\nbet ne tappe atrasti/ tapehz tap-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 63,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Atirsatus fazztja\ntecin: Ka teem ne bij ehft\ntahs wiﬀswiehtas Swehtiba-\nkamehr weens Preesteris zeltō\nar to Urim un Tumin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 64,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiſſa tchi Draudse b-\nweenā Rohpā/ tchetrdeﬁmits\ndiwi tuhkſtoschi/ trihſfimts\nfeſchdeﬁmits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 65,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bes winnu Kalpeem/\nKalponehn/ to paschu bija fept-\ntuhkſtochi/ trihſtimts trihsd-\nmits un feptini/ un teem b-\ndiwifimts Dseedataji un Di-\ndatajas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 66,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winno Sirgu bija fe-\ntinsimts trihsdeﬁmits un feſ-\ndiwifimts tchetrdeﬁmits un p-\nzi Sirg-Ehsetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 67,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tschetrſimts trihsdeﬁmi-\nun peez Kametu/feſch tuhkſtoſ-\nfeptinsimts un diwidesmits O-\nſetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 68,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un zitti no teemangſte\nTehweem/ kad tee nahze us\nKUNGA Namunu/kas Jeru-\nlemē dſihwo/ dewe no lab-\nPrahta pee ta Deewa Namu-\nka tas uszelts taptu us fa-\nWeetu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 69,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Zik tee spehje dewe tee\nMantu pee ta Darba feſch r-\ndeſmits tuhkſtochas un tuhſ-\ntchas Draknas Selta/ un .p-\ntuhkſtoschus Mahrzixus Su-\nraba/ un ſunts Preest-\nSwahrkus.\n"
